OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776888354
OL,3,CRecord race times and turnout at the
OL,4,C2026 Guernsey Marathon
OL,6,FIsland records were smashed at the
OL,7,FGuernsey Marathon on Sunday (19 April)
OL,8,Fas the fastest-ever times for men and
OL,9,Fwomen were set.
OL,11,FGuillaume Ruel crossed the line first
OL,12,Fwith a time of 2:25:00, while Harriet
OL,13,FCarr finished with 2:26:10 on the
OL,14,Fclock.
OL,16,FThe event also saw 310 people run the
OL,17,Ffull 26.25 mile course - the highest
OL,18,Fnumber in the race's history.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
