PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776888354
OL,3,CRecord race times and turnout at the
OL,4,C2026 Guernsey Marathon
OL,6,FGuillaume, who hails from France, has
OL,7,Fform across the islands, winning both
OL,8,Fthe Jersey and Guernsey marathons in
OL,9,F2024.
OL,11,F"Last year, my previous record was
OL,12,Fbroken, so I told myself this year I
OL,13,Fneed to take back the record," Ruel
OL,14,Ftold ITV News.
OL,16,F"The mission was accomplished. I
OL,17,Freally like the Jersey and Guernsey
OL,18,Fmarathons, and I do both of them every
OL,19,Fyear.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776888354
OL,3,CRecord race times and turnout at the
OL,4,C2026 Guernsey Marathon
OL,6,F"Guernsey is really hilly at the
OL,7,Fbeginning, but then you run in really
OL,8,Fbeautiful landscapes."
OL,10,FUK elite runner Harriet appeared to be
OL,11,Fequally impressed by her surroundings
OL,12,Fwhile completing the route in record
OL,13,Ftime.
OL,15,F"That was the most beautiful course
OL,16,FI've ever done," she explained.
OL,18,F"I came here to break three hours, I
OL,19,Fdid that, and it just so happened to
OL,20,Ftake the top female spot - the race
OL,21,Fcouldn't have gone any better.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776888354
OL,3,CRecord race times and turnout at the
OL,4,C2026 Guernsey Marathon
OL,6,F"I took a swim at the Venus pool on
OL,7,FLithou Island on Saturday, and thought
OL,8,FI would have a long run on Sunday.
OL,9,FI've had a lovely weekend."
OL,11,FAside from the Channel Islands,
OL,12,Frunners also came from the UK, France,
OL,13,Fthe Netherlands, the United States and
OL,14,Feven Australia.
OL,16,F"It's been incredible to see how the
OL,17,FGuernsey Marathon has grown year on
OL,18,Fyear," Andrew Thomas, the Race
OL,19,FDirector said, "with record
OL,20,Fparticipation in 2026 demonstrating
OL,21,Fthe strength and appeal of the event.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776888354
OL,3,CRecord race times and turnout at the
OL,4,C2026 Guernsey Marathon
OL,6,F"It's fantastic to see so many locals
OL,7,Ftaking part in their home race,
OL,8,Falongside runners from across the UK
OL,9,Fand beyond.
OL,11,F"Events like this play an important
OL,12,Frole in supporting the island's
OL,13,Ftourism and local economy, bringing
OL,14,Fvisitors into our hotels, restaurants
OL,15,Fand businesses while showcasing
OL,16,FGuernsey on an international stage."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
